advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-14 = Keep pressure up, target is close to collapse.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-15 = Team, status check. Who is in contact?
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-16 = Operation continues. Stay sharp.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-17 = Report received, moving to the next sector.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-18 = Breach team, report status.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-19 = Keep medics behind the front line.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-20 = Boarding party, status report.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-veteran-21 = We move on my signal.
